                    <span class="word">Physical Violence:</span> Any abuse or violence with physical contact<br>
                    <span class="word">Cruelty:</span><br><em>a)</em> The blatant disregard of another<br> <em>b)</em> The intentional infliction of pain and suffering on another<br>
                    <span class="word">Trust:</span> The knowledge that one's decisions will be taken into account by another<br>
